<p>I am having a problem in configuring ContentNegotiatingViewResolver in spring webservice. Different resources (over the net as well as books) indicate that it should be configured as:</p>  <pre><code>&lt;bean  class="org.springframework.web.servlet.view.ContentNegotiatingViewResolver"&gt;    &lt;property name="mediaTypes"&gt;      &lt;map&gt;        &lt;entry key="json" value="application/json"/&gt;        &lt;entry key="xml" value="text/xml"/&gt;      &lt;/map&gt;   &lt;/property&gt;   &lt;property name="defaultContentType" value="text/html"/&gt; &lt;/bean&gt; </code></pre>  <p>But the compiler complains that ContentNegotiatingViewResolver class does not have the property(set method) for mediaTypes. When I go for the documentation of this class; actually there is no such property or setter method.</p>  <p>How to go around this? Am I missing some thing?</p>